You need ACE (http://www.cse.wustl.edu/~schmidt/ACE.html), packaged as
`libace` in modern distributions

You need vast from https://github.com/jonathlela/vast

Vast Installation:

     git clone git://github.com/jonathlela/vast.git
     git checkout cmake
     cmake .
     make 
     (make install)

librecube installation
     git clone git://github.com/jonathlela/librecube.git
     cmake .
     make
